    "To sum up, ML involves teaching computers to make predictions or decisions based on data.",
    "This is accomplished by using algorithms that adjust parameters such as weights and biases in a model that maps inputs to outputs through multiple layers of artificial neurons.",
    "These algorithms can be supervised or unsupervised, use reinforcement learning, etc.",
    "A loss function is a measure of how well a ML model fits the training data.",
    "It calculates the 102 Page 10 of 36 difference between the predicted output and the actual value."
